data.label: MSDK / MobileGame Software Development Kit
data.description: MSDK，全称 MobileGame Software Development Kit，是增值服务部为游戏（主要为手游）提供公共组件和服务库的平台，旨在加快游戏接入各公共组件和海外开放平台。

data.label: MSDK / MobileGame Software Development Kit
data.description: MSDK, full name MobileGame Software Development Kit, is a platform provided by the Value-Added Services Department for games (mainly mobile games) to provide public components and service libraries, aiming to accelerate game access to public components and overseas open platforms.
